[2026-07-11] BASELINE: Golden Baseline is MODEL-DERIVED, not compiler-derived —
    no `cobc` is available in this sandbox. This is disclosed in audit_report.md
    §5 and cobol/SEMANTICS.md "Gate note". Equivalence claims are therefore
